    <p>
 Hello! I'm Anamta , a passionate UI/UX and a web designer student dedicated to creating intutive and 
 engaging digital experiences . My journey into the world of design began with a fascination for how 
 thoughtful design can transform user interactions and solve real-world problems.  
 Currently pursuing my studies in bachelors of vocation (web designing) at kalindi college Delhi
